TI  - Why "formal" climate adaptation strategies fail in sub-Saharan Africa: Ignoring adapters' agency in the case of smallholding agriculture farming practices in Bono East Region of Ghana
T2  - CLIMATE RESILIENCE AND SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
