TI  - Strengthening climate adaptation in the northern region of Ghana: insights from a stakeholder analysis
T2  - CLIMATE POLICY
LA  - English
KW  - Stakeholder collaboration
KW  - climate adaptation
KW  - smallholder farmers
KW  - conservation agriculture
KW  - Ghana
KW  - CHALLENGES
