TI  - Climate Resilience and Coffee Farmers' Welfare in Central Aceh, Indonesia: Adaptation Strategies from the Maqasid al-Shari'ah Perspective
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF ISLAMIC FINANCE AND SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT-IJIFSD
