TI  - Relevant drivers of farmers' decision behavior regarding their adaptation to climate change: a case study of two regions in Cote d'Ivoire
T2  - MITIGATION AND ADAPTATION STRATEGIES FOR GLOBAL CHANGE
LA  - English
KW  - Adaptation behavior
