TI  - Exploring the effects of precipitation perception, perceived risk, and irrigation facility quality on farmers' climate-adaptive farming practices: Evidence from continuous straw returning in China
T2  - ENVIRONMENT DEVELOPMENT AND SUSTAINABILITY
