TI  - Climate and Land Use Change Pressures on Food Production in Social-Ecological Systems: Perceptions from Farmers in Village Tank Cascade Systems of Sri Lanka
T2  - SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - climate change
KW  - land use change
KW  - farmers' perceptions
KW  - perception determinants
KW  - Village Tank Cascade Systems
