TI  - Soil and Water Management Practices as a Strategy to Cope with Climate Change Effects in Smallholder Potato Production in the Eastern Highlands of Ethiopia
T2  - SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - fertilizer
KW  - irrigation
KW  - moisture stress
KW  - nutrient depletion
KW  - rainfall variability
