TI  - An intersectional analysis of the collective efficacy-drought adaptation nexus among small-scale farmers in uMkhanyakude District Municipality, South Africa
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL SOCIOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Small-scale farmers
