TI  - Economic impact of climate change on farmers' income in Ramanathapuram district: A ricardian analysis
T2  - INDIAN JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURAL SCIENCES
LA  - English
KW  - Keywords : Climate change
KW  - Climate trend
KW  - Employment
KW  - Ricardian analysis
