TI  - Determinants of the Adoption of Climate-Smart Agricultural Practices by Small-Scale Farming Households in King Cetshwayo District Municipality, South Africa
T2  - SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - adaptation
KW  - climate change
