TI  - Farmers' preferences and willingness to pay for climate-resilient crop insurance: heterogeneity analysis using a discrete choice experiment in Northwest Ethiopia
T2  - ENVIRONMENT DEVELOPMENT AND SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - Climate resilience
KW  - Crop insurance
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Discrete choice experiment
