TI  - Climate change impacts and the rice farmers' responses at irrigated upstream and downstream in Indonesia
T2  - HELIYON
LA  - English
KW  - Perception
KW  - Knowledge
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Adaptation
KW  - Irrigation
KW  - ADAPTATION BEHAVIOR
KW  - LOCAL KNOWLEDGE
