TI  - UNDERSTANDING THE REPRESENTATION OF PASTORALISM IN LIVESTOCK-RELATED CLIMATE ADAPTATION POLICIES IN GHANA AND NIGERIA:A REVIEW OF KEY POLICY DOCUMENTS
T2  - NOMADIC PEOPLES
