TI  - Perception, experience, and indigenous knowledge of climate change and variability: the case of Accra, a sub-Saharan African city
T2  - REGIONAL ENVIRONMENTAL CHANGE
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Climate variability
KW  - Perceptions
KW  - Indigenous knowledge
KW  - Urban
