TI  - Implementing climate variability adaptation at the community level in the Amazon floodplain
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE & POLICY
LA  - English
KW  - Local ecological knowledge
KW  - Adaptation
KW  - Policy making
KW  - Environmental governance
