TI  - Sustainable integrated farming system model for enhancing profitability, resource efficiency, and soil health for smallholders in the Indian Mediterranean ecosystem of the North-Western Himalayan region
T2  - FRONTIERS IN SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
