TI  - The role of indigenous knowledge in climate change adaptation in Africa
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE & POLICY
LA  - English
KW  - Indigenous and local knowledge
KW  - Africa
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Adaptation
KW  - Bibliometric analysis
