TI  - Pathways from climate change to emotional wellbeing: A qualitative study of Kenyan smallholder farmers living with HIV
T2  - PLOS GLOBAL PUBLIC HEALTH
LA  - English
KW  - MENTAL-HEALTH
KW  - ECOLOGICAL GRIEF
KW  - SOCIAL DETERMINANTS
