TI  - The insight of agricultural adaptation to climate change: a case of rice growers in Eastern Himalaya, India
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF BIOMETEOROLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - India
KW  - Eastern Himalaya
KW  - Adaptation
KW  - MNL model
