TI  - Determinants of adaptation choices to climate change by sheep and goat farmers in Northern Ethiopia: the case of Southern and Central Tigray, Ethiopia
T2  - SPRINGERPLUS
LA  - English
KW  - Sheep
KW  - Goat
KW  - Climate change
