TI  - The Impact of Climate Change on Agricultural Risks in Southern Africa: A Case Study of Mutoko District, Zimbabwe
T2  - RESEARCH ON WORLD AGRICULTURAL ECONOMY
LA  - English
KW  - Agricultural Risks
KW  - Climate Change
KW  - Rural Zimbabwe
