TI  - EXERCISING RICARDIAN EMPIRICS TO INVESTIGATE THE IMPACT OF CLIMATE CHANGE ON DAIRY PRODUCTION IN PAKISTAN
T2  - FRESENIUS ENVIRONMENTAL BULLETIN
