TI  - Social-ecological vulnerability of small-scale farming in the southern Andes: the role of Indigenous and Local Ecological Knowledge in adaptation to climate variability
T2  - FRONTIERS IN SUSTAINABLE FOOD SYSTEMS
LA  - English
