TI  - Farmers' fertilizer use and climate change perceptions: Their impact on crop output in the yellow river basin: A structural equation modeling study
T2  - ENVIRONMENT DEVELOPMENT AND SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - Protection Motivation Theory
KW  - Theory of Planned Behavior
KW  - Structural Equation Modeling Approach
KW  - Climate Change Resilience
