TI  - Innovative approach to build a "no regret" framework for reinforcing agricultural water resilience under climate risks and change in Burkina Faso
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF CLIMATE CHANGE STRATEGIES AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Resilience
