TI  - Assessment of the use of Participatory Integrated Climate Services for Agriculture (PICSA) approach by farmers to manage climate risk in Mali and Senegal
T2  - CLIMATE SERVICES
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Climate information services
KW  - Climate variability
KW  - Food security
KW  - Livelihood options
